[normal]&#xa0;[bold]6  [bold]How[bold] should the legislation governing level crossings be updated?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]1
[normal]6
[normal].  
[normal]The Department recognises that the 
[normal]current law on level crossings is 
[normal]antiquated, 
[normal]comple
[normal]x an
[normal]d inaccessible
