[normal] 
[normal]For this reason the Department, in collaboration with the 
[normal]O
[normal]ffice of 
[normal]R
[normal]ail 
[normal]R
[normal]egulation, 
[normal]put forward a proposal to the Law Commission for
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]a 
[normal]comprehensive 
[normal]review of level crossing legislation.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] In June 2008, the Law Commission announced tha
[normal]t this review would take place 
[normal]as part of its 10th programme of law reform.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] 
[normal]Following public consultation, t
[normal]he 
[normal]Law 
[normal]Commission expects to publish 
[normal]its recommendations
[normal] later in 2013
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]1
[normal]7
[normal].  
[normal]The Department, together with the Office of Rail Regulation, will 
[normal]need to consider the Law Commission’s proposals in detail before responding.
